snippet: Texas announced Monday that it was cutting off Medicaid funding to Planned Parenthood clinics after undercover videos that featured discussions about fetal tissue.
abstract: Texas plans to end Medicaid funding to Planned Parenthood clinics following release of video footage concerning sale of fetal tissue for profit by clinics; controversial footage prompted lawmakers in Louisiana to take judicial action as well.
lead_paragraph: Texas announced Monday that it was cutting off Medicaid funding to Planned Parenthood clinics after undercover videos that featured discussions about fetal tissue.

headline.print_headline: More Sparring Over Planned Parenthood Funds
